/", "3/united states/nevada/nye/tonopah/"], "contributor": ["university of nevada las vegas university libraries"], "date": "1908-01-19", "dates": ["1908-01-19"], "description": ["I n nr r i TOXOPAH DAILY BONANZA TOXOPAH NEVADA JANUARY 10 1008 l t V l in iii s in TONOPAH DAILY BONANZA Published Every Morning Monaay Excepted at Tonopah Nevada W W BOOTH Editor and Proprietor UNIONjbLABEL J S DAVELER Manager Member of Associated Press TERMS OP SUBSCRIPTION ne year fllOSI Three months Nine months 100 One month tlx months 76 One week Subscriptions by mail mu st be paid for in advance 350 TEN DOLLARS REWARD A reward of 10 Will be paid for In formation that will lead to the arrest and conviction of parties stealing The Bonanza from premises of subscribers TO SUBSCRIBERS Parties who do not receive their papers or who have any cause of com print will oblige by notifying this office Entered at the Postofflce in Tonopah a second class matter EDITORIAL COMMENT CONDITIONS ARE IMPROVING Bradstreets and Duns reports for the week declare that there Is a better feeling in the financial world These two commercial agencies Keep their fingers on the financial pulse with their branches in every city town and hamlet in the United States and correspondents in all the European cities and it is well to give heed"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2023-06-30T14:51:37.705Z", "group": ["ndnp/nvln", "university-of-nevada-las-vegas-university-libraries-awardee"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/resource/sn86076142/1908-01-19/ed-1/?sp=4", "image_url": ["https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:nvln:batch_nvln_aurora_ver02:data:sn86076142:00415626940:1908011901:0075/full/pct:6.25/0/default.jpg#h=416&w=277", "https://tile.loc.gov/image-services/iiif/service:ndnp:nvln:batch_nvln_aurora_ver02:data:sn86076142:00415626940:1908011901:0075/full/pct:12.5/0/default.jpg#h=832&w=555", "https://tile.loc.gov/text-services/word-coordinates-service?segment=/service/ndnp/nvln